{"text_id":132248,"tokens":["How"," to"," Handle"," People"," With"," Anxiety"," Problems","\n\n","Handling"," people"," with"," anxiety"," problems"," requires"," empathy",","," understanding",","," and"," patience","."," Anxiety"," disorders"," can"," be"," overwhelming"," and"," debilitating",","," and"," it","'","s"," essential"," to"," know"," how"," to"," support"," your"," loved"," one","."," This"," article"," will"," guide"," you"," on"," how"," to"," handle"," people"," with"," anxiety"," problems",".","\n\n","**","Stay"," Calm","**","\n\n","When"," dealing"," with"," someone"," who"," has"," an"," anxiety"," problem",","," it","'","s"," crucial"," to"," remain"," calm"," and"," composed","."," Avoid"," getting"," frustrated"," or"," annoyed",","," as"," this"," can"," exacerbate"," the"," situation","."," Instead",","," speak"," in"," a"," gentle"," and"," soothing"," tone"," to"," help"," them"," feel"," more"," at"," ease",".","\n\n","**","Take"," Your"," Loved"," One"," Somewhere"," Quiet"," and"," Sit"," Them"," Down","**","\n\n","Sometimes",","," people"," with"," anxiety"," problems"," can"," feel"," overwhelmed"," by"," their"," surroundings","."," Take"," them"," to"," a"," quiet"," room"," or"," a"," peaceful"," spot"," outside"," where"," they"," can"," feel"," more"," comfortable","."," Sit"," them"," down"," and"," encourage"," them"," to"," take"," slow",","," deep"," breaths",".","\n\n","**","Offer"," Medication","**","\n\n","If"," your"," loved"," one"," has"," prescribed"," medication"," for"," their"," anxiety",","," encourage"," them"," to"," take"," it","."," However",","," avoid"," pushing"," them"," to"," take"," medication"," if"," they","'","re"," not"," willing","."," It","'","s"," essential"," to"," respect"," their"," autonomy"," and"," decisions"," regarding"," their"," treatment",".","\n\n","**","Tell"," Her"," That"," She"," Is"," Safe","**","\n\n","Re","assure"," your"," loved"," one"," that"," they"," are"," safe"," and"," t