 care"," of"," their"," physical"," health",".","\n\n","**","Allocate"," Time"," for"," Worry","ing","**","\n\n","Allocate"," a"," specific"," time"," each"," day"," for"," your"," loved"," one"," to"," worry"," and"," express"," their"," concerns","."," This"," can"," help"," them"," feel"," heard"," and"," validated","."," Listen"," to"," their"," worries"," without"," judgment"," and"," offer"," support",".","\n\n","**","Validate"," Her"," Feelings","**","\n\n","Validation"," is"," crucial"," when"," dealing"," with"," people"," with"," anxiety"," problems","."," Let"," your"," loved"," one"," know"," that"," their"," feelings"," are"," valid"," and"," that"," you"," understand"," their"," anxiety"," is"," real",".","\n\n","**","Offer"," Human"," Touch","**","\n\n","Human"," touch"," can"," be"," comforting"," for"," people"," with"," anxiety"," problems","."," Offer"," hugs",","," hold"," hands",","," or"," give"," massages"," to"," help"," them"," feel"," more"," relaxed",".","\n\n","**","Accept"," That"," Her"," Needs"," Are"," Different","**","\n\n","People"," with"," anxiety"," problems"," have"," different"," needs"," than"," others","."," Accept"," that"," they"," may"," need"," more"," time"," to"," accomplish"," tasks",","," may"," avoid"," certain"," situations",","," or"," require"," more"," support",".","\n\n","**","Encourage"," Him"," to"," Seek"," Professional"," Help","**","\n\n","Encourage"," your"," loved"," one"," to"," seek"," professional"," help"," from"," a"," therapist",","," counselor",","," or"," psychologist","."," Mental"," health"," professionals"," can"," provide"," them"," with"," the"," tools"," and"," strategies"," they"," need"," to"," manage"," their"," anxiety",".","\n\n","**","Form"," a"," Support"," Network","**","\n\n","Form"," a"," support"," network"," of"," family",","," friends",","," and"," mental"," health"," professionals"," to"," help"," your"," loved"," one"," feel"," supported"," and"," understood",".","\n\n","**","Remember"," That"," You"," Are"," Not"," Responsible"," for"," Anyone","'","s"," Health","**","\n\n","It","'","s"," essential"," to"," remember"," that"," you","'","re"," not"," responsible"," for"," your"," loved"," one","'","s"," health","."," Avoid"," taking"," on"," too"," much"," responsibility"," and"," encourage"," them"," to"," take"," ownership"," of"," their"," anxiety"," management",".","\n\n","**","Practice"," Self","-","Care","**","\n\n","Managing"," people"," with"," anxiety"," problems"," can"," be"," draining","."," Practice"," self","-","care"," by"," taking"," time"," for"," yourself",","," engaging"," in"," relaxation"," techniques",","," and"," seeking"," support"," from"," others",".","\n\n","**","Use"," Your"," Own"," Support"," Network","**","\n\n","Don","'","t"," be"," afraid"," to"," use"," your"," own"," support"," network"," to"," get"," help"," and"," guidance","."," Seek"," advice"," from"," mental"," health"," professionals",","," support"," groups",","," or"," online"," resources"," to"," help"," you"," cope"," with"," the"," demands"," of"," supporting"," someone"," with"," an"," anxiety"," problem",".","\n\n","**","Consult"," a"," Psychologist"," Independ","ently"," If"," You"," Feel"," Over","whelmed","**","\n\n","If"," you","'","re"," feeling"," overwhelmed"," or"," unsure"," of"," how"," to"," support"," your"," loved"," one",","," consider"," consulting"," a"," psychologist"," independently","."," They"," can"," provide"," you"," with"," guidance",","," support",","," and"," strategies"," to"," help"," you"," cope",".","\n\n","**","Understand"," That"," an"," Anxiety"," Disorder"," Is"," a"," Mental"," Illness","**","\n\n","Anxiety"," disorders"," are"," mental"," illnesses"," that"," affect"," daily"," functioning"," and"," quality"," of"," life","."," They","'","re"," not"," something"," that"," people"," can"," simply"," \"","snap"," out"," of",".\"","\n\n","**","Know"," the"," Difference"," Between"," Anxiety"," and"," a"," D